title: TIP-3: Implementing USDT price feed to the list of supported assets on Thales
body:
https://gov.thales.io/docs/TIP-3

TIP-3 proposes adding the Tether (USDT) price feed from Chainlink to Thales and enabling USDT market creation.

Adding a USDT price feed from Chainlink to the list of supported assets on Thales will enable users to create, trade, and exercise USDT markets, expanding the platform’s current possibilities.

Are you in favor of this proposal?
author: 0x11219d61e95fC5930762b16868dDB2C9c6fc83fA
